Class PacketInfoEmployee

java.lang.Object
fr.univtours.polytech.punchingcommon.model.PacketInfoEmployee
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class PacketInfoEmployee extends Object implements Serializable
Class which contains the information of the employee. A PacketInfoEmployee is sent by the server as an answer of the check of an employee.
